structure

Class Repository

  • java.lang.Object
    • structure.Repository

  • public class Repository
extends java.lang.Object
    Defines the data structure that represents a repository in GitHub. It is up to the programmer to ensure that the information is consistent with that on GitHub.
    Author:
    ZiXian92
